<plot>A story that would seem trivial and common at first. An assassin hired to kill the husband of a more than desperate wife, not surprisingly for money. A game of greed, where everyone wants it all, everyone but the victim. A story that takes one to twisted places and minds, an invitation to the surreal. An ethic dilemma of a man with no morals and a woman equally without rationality, all happening in the face of the wicked and lost mind of an utterly broken man.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?399829</url></doc>
